&lt;p>A complete research platform for AI-assisted endovascular intervention, spanning preoperative 3D planning through intraoperative RL-guided navigation.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Pipeline:&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>CTA → STL&lt;/strong> — TotalSegmentator vessel segmentation, VMTK centerline extraction&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>SOFA FEM Simulation&lt;/strong> — Cosserat beam guidewire model, realistic vascular deformation&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>RL Navigation&lt;/strong> — SAC/PPO agents with geodesic distance reward + safety constraints&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Biplane DSA&lt;/strong> — DLT triangulation + Beer-Lambert X-ray projection for 2D-3D registration&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Intraoperative Correction&lt;/strong> — SE(3) IRC-RL with real DSA feedback&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Ongoing research:&lt;/strong> Training a diffusion-based trajectory planner on large-scale SOFA-generated synthetic data, transferring to real vascular geometries — targeting to overcome clinical data scarcity.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Affiliations:&lt;/strong> Tongji University × PKU DLIB | 2026&lt;/p>
